The paper proposes a novel metric learning method that leverages convolutional neural networks to evaluate distance between graphs. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper applies the proposed method to functional brain networks, indicating that it may also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), social and information networks (cs.SI), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
